rre, son père, Thomas Mosell, avait 26 ans et sa mère, Margareth Visedolou, avait 22 ans. Elle a épousé Edmund Stratton en 1436, à Shotley, Suffolk, Angleterre. Ils ont eu au moins 3 fils et 2 filles. Elle est décédée en 1476, dans sa ville natale, à l’âge de 61 ans, et a été enterrée à Shotley, Suffolk, Angleterre."},"de":{"1415–1476":"1415–1476","1420–1500":"1420–1500","1410–1476":"1410–1476","1436–1485":"1436–1485","1438–Female":"1438–Verstorben","1440–1498":"1440–1498","1442–Male":"1442–Verstorben","1445–1485":"1445–1485","1389–1419":"1389–1419","1393–1421":"1393–1421","1440":"1440","1393":"1393","1415":"1415","1436":"1436","1445":"1445","1500":"1500","1455":"1455","1389":"1389","1421":"1421","1476":"1476","1498":"1498","1410":"1410","1442":"1442","1420":"1420","about 1414":"um 1414","1485":"1485","about 1445":"um 1445","about 1442":"um 1442","1419":"1419","1438":"1438","Ipswich, Suffolk, England":"Ipswich, Suffolk, England","Shotley, Suffolk, England":"Shotley, Suffolk, England","lifeSummary":"Als Margareth Mosell 1415 in Shotley, Suffolk, England geboren wurde, war ihr Vater Thomas Mosell 26 und ihre Mutter Margareth Visedolou 22. Sie hat 1436 in Shotley, Suffolk, England Edmund Stratton geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 3 Söhne und 2 Töchter. Sie starb 1476 im Alter von 61 Jahren in ihrem Geburtsort und wurde in Shotley, Suffolk, England begraben."},"ht":{"1415–1476":"1415–1476","1420–1500":"1420–1500","1410–1476":"1410–1476","1436–1485":"1436–1485","1438–Female":"1438–Desede","1440–1498":"1440–1498","1442–Male":"1442–Desede","1445–1485":"1445–1485","1389–1419":"1389–1419","1393–1421":"1393–1421","1440":"1440","1393":"1393","1415":"1415","1436":"1436","1445":"1445","1500":"1500","1455":"1455","1389":"1389","1421":"1421","1476":"1476","1498":"1498","1410":"1410","1442":"1442","1420":"1420","about 1414":"about 1414","1485":"1485","about 1445":"about 1445","about 1442":"about 1442","1419":"1419","1438":"1438","Ipswich, Suffolk, England":"Ipswich, Suffolk, Englan